  <brief_title>LVHR Multicenter Study</brief_title>
  <official_title>Randomized Controlled National Multicenter Study for Evaluation of Two Different Ways of Fixation of Mesh-implants and Differences With or Without Approximation of Herniadefects at Laparoscopic Operation for Incisional and Ventral Hernia</official_title>
